The paper proposes a new method for Vietnamese dependency parsing using LSTM and pre-trained word embeddings, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The use of deep neural network models and pre-trained embeddings also suggests that the paper could be relevant to sub-categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of character-level word embeddings, which could also make it relevant to cs.CV (Computer Vision) sub-category.
